f(x)\in\Bbb Z[x]\,
\,a/b,\,
\,\gcd(a,b)=1.
0 = f(a/b)\ \Rightarrow\ 0 = b^n f(a/b)\ =\, f_n a^n + f_{n-1} a^{n-1}b+\cdots+f_1 ab^{n-1} + f_0 b^n
\,\ (\overbrace{f_{n} a^{n-1}+f_{n-1}a^{n-2}b+\cdots+f_1 b^{n-1}}^{\large\rm an\ integer,\ since\,\ \color{#c00}{f_i\ are\ integers}})\,a\,=\, -f_0 b^n,\ 
\ a\mid b^n f_0\,\color{#0a0}{\Rightarrow}\, a\mid f_0,\ 
\,\gcd(a,b)=1,\,\ a\mid bc\,\Rightarrow\,a\mid c,\,
\,a\mid b^nc\,\color{#0a0}{\Rightarrow}\,a\mid c.
\,\color{#c00}{f_i\,\ \rm being\ integers},\,
\,a\mid b^n f_0.\,
\, b\mid a^n f_n\,\Rightarrow\,b\mid f_n.
\,x-c/d\,
\,c/d\,
\qquad (x-c/d)\,(x-d/c)\, =\, x^2-(c/d+d/c)\,x + 1\,
\,c/d\,
